text: James Reid (born 1 August 1992) is a South African mountain bike racer. He rode at the cross-country event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. He finished in 42nd place after crashing out. ==References== Category:South African male cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of South Africa Category:1992 births Category:Living people
